j)	Assurer l’administration du projet : (A partir du mois de janvier 2024 en décembre 2025).

The project includes following activities:
1.  Creation of farmers’ groups and training farmers on nurseries and tree planting techniques: December 2023 –February 2024;
 2. Establishing community nurseries in local villages and raising seedlings in nurseries: March-November 2024 and February- November 2025;
3. Preparing the restoration sites: September- November 2024 and September- November 2025;
4. Distribution of seedlings to local farmers: November-December 2024 and November-December 2025;
5. Planting seedlings on restoration sites: December – January 2024 and December 2025;
6. Monitoring and maintenance of planted trees:  January 2026-December 2029.
